			<br>
		<<default>>
			一个钱包在<<bhis>>的<<if $monster is 1>>爪子<<else>>嘴巴<</if>>里。可能是<<bHe>>偷来的，但里面可能有钱或其他贵重物品。<<bHe>>把它放在你脚边，然后看着你，等待你的反应。
			<br><br>
			<<link [[拿走它|Bird Tower Wallet]]>><<bird_loot valuables 20>><<npcincr "Great Hawk" love 1>><<transform bird 1>><<bird_stockholm 1>><</link>><<gbirdstockholm>><<glove>>
			<br>
		<</switch>>
		<<link [[责骂|Bird Tower Valuables Scold]]>><<bird_loot valuables -20>><<npcincr "Great Hawk" dom -1>><<transform bird 1>><<bird_stockholm 1>><</link>><<gbirdstockholm>><<ldom>>
		<br>
		<<link [[无动于衷|Bird Tower Valuables Nothing]]>><<bird_loot valuables -10>><<npcincr "Great Hawk" love -1>><</link>><<llove>>
		<br>
	<<case "food">>
		<<bHe>>抓着
		<<rng 10>>
		<<switch $rng>>
		<<case 1>>
			吃了一半的糕点<<set $bird_food to "pasty">>
		<<case 2>>
			一个甜甜圈<<set $bird_food to "donut">>
		<<case 3>>
			一袋坚果<<set $bird_food to "nuts">>
		<<case 4>>
			一包薯片<<set $bird_food to "crisps">>
		<<case 5>>
			一个大巧克力棒<<set $bird_food to "chocolate">>
		<<case 6>>
			一个苹果<<set $bird_food to "apple">>
		<<case 7>>
			一根胡萝卜<<set $bird_food to "carrot">>
		<<case 8>>
			一罐烤豆<<set $bird_food to "beans">>
		<<case 9>>
			一罐金枪鱼<<set $bird_food to "tuna">>
		<<default>>
			一罐蛋奶冻<<set $bird_food to "custard">>
		<</switch>>
		在<<bhis>>的<<if $monster is 1>>爪子<<else>>嘴<</if>>里.
		<<if $monster is 1>>
			"<<print either(
			"我看见没有翅膀的人在吃这些东西。",
			"也许更符合你的口味?",
			"给你的食物。",
			"不懂陆地人的口味，但对你来说……",
			"没有翅膀的鸟儿没有人看守它们的食物，真可怜。",
			"从很远的地方闻到。很容易拿。",
			"从陆地上捡来的。今天没有猎物。"
			)>>"
		<</if>>
		<<bHe>>把它放在你脚边，然后看着你，等待你的反应。
		<br><br>

		<<link [[吃|Bird Tower Food]]>><<bird_loot food 20>><<npcincr "Great Hawk" love 1>><<transform bird 1>><<bird_stockholm 1>><</link>><<gbirdstockholm>><<glove>><<lhunger>>
		<br>
		<<link [[责骂|Bird Tower Food Scold]]>><<bird_loot food -20>><<npcincr "Great Hawk" dom -1>><<transform bird 1>><<def 1>><<bird_stockholm 1>><</link>><<gbirdstockholm>><<ldom>>
		<br>
		<<link [[无动于衷|Bird Tower Food Nothing]]>><<bird_loot food -10>><<npcincr "Great Hawk" love -1>><</link>><<llove>>
		<br>
	<<default>>
		<<bHe>>抓着
		<<select_random_clothes>>
		<<if setup.clothes[_random_slot][_random_index].plural isnot 1>>
