			<<link [[穿|Bird Tower Clothes]]>><<generalWear _random_slot _random_index>><<bird_loot clothes 20>><<npcincr "Great Hawk" love 1>><<transform bird 1>><<bird_stockholm 1>><</link>><<gbirdstockholm>><<glove>>
